<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:54:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>价格暴跌令持有者不安，摩根士丹利推出比特币 ETF</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/morgan-stanley-debuts-bitcoin-etf-as-price-slump-rattles-holders</link><description>摩根士丹利将成为第一家推出自己的比特币追踪交易所交易基金的华尔街银行，这是数字资产生态系统的一个里程碑，凸显了原始加密货币已经深深融入金融主流——即使其周围的市场已经降温。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQiKNwsr62dE/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:12:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/morgan-stanley-debuts-bitcoin-etf-as-price-slump-rattles-holders</guid></item><item><title>美伊停火计划推动比特币跃升至三周高位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/bitcoin-jumps-to-three-week-high-on-us-iran-ceasefire-plan</link><description>美国和伊朗同意初步停火后，比特币升至三周高位，促使风险资产飙升。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igeBnNNJht2I/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/bitcoin-jumps-to-three-week-high-on-us-iran-ceasefire-plan</guid></item><item><title>白宫经济学家表示稳定币奖励不会损害银行</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/white-house-economists-says-stablecoin-rewards-won-t-harm-banks</link><description>白宫经济学家在周三的一份报告中表示，禁止加密货币公司向客户提供稳定币收益不会对社区银行产生有意义的影响，这标志着两个行业之间激烈冲突的最新进展，该冲突已导致国会立法陷入停滞。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV3Gy8fSExP4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/white-house-economists-says-stablecoin-rewards-won-t-harm-banks</guid></item><item><title>币安创始人回忆录详细介绍了 Gensler 早期的关系和入狱时间</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/binance-founder-s-memoir-details-early-gensler-ties-prison-time</link><description>赵长鹏在承认反洗钱和违反美国制裁行为之前，将币安打造成全球最大的加密货币交易所，他在周二出版的回忆录中讲述了他对公司法律危机的看法。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiSzNMP5yOyQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 01:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-08/binance-founder-s-memoir-details-early-gensler-ties-prison-time</guid></item><item><title>MrBeast 的数字化推动遭遇了持怀疑态度的伊丽莎白·沃伦 (Elizabeth Warren)</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-07/mrbeast-s-digital-push-runs-into-a-skeptical-elizabeth-warren</link><description>改善 YouTube 一代的财务未来。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is41fjn3VToM/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-07/mrbeast-s-digital-push-runs-into-a-skeptical-elizabeth-warren</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势缓解后比特币收窄损失</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-07/bitcoin-slides-with-risk-assets-as-trump-s-iran-ultimatum-looms</link><description>尽管唐纳德·特朗普总统的关键停火期限临近，但随着投资者对外交解决中东冲突抱有希望，比特币减少了损失。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iT9YTH88rZiI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 05:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-07/bitcoin-slides-with-risk-assets-as-trump-s-iran-ultimatum-looms</guid></item><item><title>币安合规人员离开金融犯罪、监控岗位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/binance-compliance-staff-leave-financial-crime-monitoring-roles</link><description>当币安于 2023 年底承认美国制裁和反洗钱违规行为时，重建合规业务是交易的关键。该交易所当年早些时候聘请了美国前助理检察官诺亚·帕尔曼(Noah Perlman)担任首席合规官，领导处理制裁执行、金融犯罪监测和调查的团队。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWLtYmpqzUDg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 14:50:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/binance-compliance-staff-leave-financial-crime-monitoring-roles</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 第一季度未实现亏损 145 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/strategy-posts-14-5-billion-unrealized-loss-in-first-quarter</link><description>比特币累加器 Strategy Inc. 在第一季度录得约 145 亿美元的未实现亏损，原因是 Michael Saylor 领导的公司持有的加密货币价值下跌。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPeMF1BmeKE0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 12:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/strategy-posts-14-5-billion-unrealized-loss-in-first-quarter</guid></item></channel></rss>